WEBVTT

00:07:01.720 --> 00:07:03.419
Some of the rage I felt at the time

00:07:03.443 --> 00:07:05.364
was that if roles were reversed,

00:07:05.388 --> 00:07:09.203
and an Arab, Muslim
or Muslim-appearing person

00:07:09.227 --> 00:07:14.081
had killed three white American
college students execution-style,

00:07:14.105 --> 00:07:15.261
in their home,

00:07:15.285 --> 00:07:16.779
what would we have called it?

00:07:18.041 --> 00:07:19.492
A terrorist attack.

00:07:20.304 --> 00:07:23.475
When white men commit
acts of violence in the US,

00:07:23.499 --> 00:07:24.719
they're lone wolves,

00:07:24.743 --> 00:07:25.933
mentally ill

00:07:25.957 --> 00:07:27.781
or driven by a parking dispute.